 />\nIt&rsquo;s a big house.  It&rsquo;s weird I only ever see few of you.  Almost like the studio couldn&rsquo;t afford another X-Man.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96807d091f02efc31395811da9800e094b19565f","tid":1097072,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14f0ccaf2d471be1f388db668ddfe230f3358faf","tid":1097072,"uid":170244,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T07:24:08.000Z","msg":"Tony 返黎地球,<br />\n然後所有剩低落黎嘅Avengers (包括CM) 一齊去搵Thanos 算賬,<br />\nThanos 個星球變成一片廢墟,<br />\n因為Thanos 以為消滅一半生命後宇宙會變好,<br />\n但點知反而令成個宇宙陷入一片混亂,<br />\n所以Thanos 好沮喪地毀滅咗佢原本用黎享清福嘅星球洩憤.<br />\n<br />\nAvengers 要求佢將宇宙還原,<br />\n但佢話手套爛咗做唔到,<br />\n於是正式開拖,<br />\n結果佢地都係唔夠Thanos 砌,<br />\n但Thanos 亦無意願殺死佢地.<br />\nThanos 打低完佢地後,<br />\n就將佢地transport 返地球,<br />\n叫佢地放低過去,適應新嘅世界...<br />\n<br />\n(以上為頭30分鐘嘅劇情 <span style=\"color: blue;\">推測</span>)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T07:54:15.000Z","msg":"Tony 忍唔著出口遁 成功感化Thanos<br />\n最後大團圓 BBQ結局 一係跳起 Ya"},{"pid":"b59491ebe4a451fd79c624846bab6f0389987b3a","tid":1097072,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T07:58:32.000Z","msg":"最後ant man縮少 <br />\n捐入thrones個屎眼再變大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43d3cf1c241b9b54b7190dfbb9a449ac3fe0fba","tid":1097072,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:13:34.000Z","msg":"一開頭全部人灰晒<br />\n<br />\nThor同Rocket喺某酒吧搵到女武神<br />\nThor希望搵Thanos報仇，女武神話好危險<br />\n<br />\nRocket收到Benatar嘅信號<br />\nRocket鼓勵Thor要振作，佢哋一齊負責去搵Tony<br />\n<br />\nSteve代表Avengers同全世界承諾never move on<br />\n返到AVG總部同Natasha計算失蹤同死亡的人數<br />\n然後承接Captain Marvel彩蛋<br />\nCarol見到美隊時好震驚，Avengers計劃完全超出自己想像<br />\n<br />\n去返Titan場景，Nebula表示冇人會嚟救佢哋，而Rocket係唯一可以搵到佢哋嘅人，雖然佢哋唔知對方有冇死<br />\nTony冇辦法修復Benatar，喺Pepper同埋Banner嘅描述下佢哋估到Tony同Peter去咗Titan，Thor同Rocket負責去救Tony<br />\n<br />\n佢哋首先去到Nidavellia搵到Benatar嘅逃生艙，收到Tony嘅信息<br />\n跟住救返Tony，而Rocket對Tony嘅維修技術印象深刻，兩人一拍即合<br />\n<br />\n全部人返到AVG總部，Thor以為Carol係敵人，差啲打咗出手<br />\nSteve同Tony終於見返面<br />\n<br />\n想知再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bb5b61542c2aec284b66f5b85468bf92fa70b7","tid":1097072,"uid":27689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a43d3cf1c241b9b54b7190dfbb9a449ac3fe0fba","tid":1097072,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:13:34.000Z","msg":"一開頭全部人灰晒<br />\n<br />\nThor同Rocket喺某酒吧搵到女武神<br />\nThor希望搵Thanos報仇，女武神話好危險<br />\n<br />\nRocket收到Benatar嘅信號<br />\nRocket鼓勵Thor要振作，佢哋一齊負責去搵Tony<br />\n<br />\nSteve代表Avengers同全世界承諾never move on<br />\n返到AVG總部同Natasha計算失蹤同死亡的人數<br />\n然後承接Captain Marvel彩蛋<br />\nCarol見到美隊時好震驚，Avengers計劃完全超出自己想像<br />\n<br />\n去返Titan場景，Nebula表示冇人會嚟救佢哋，而Rocket係唯一可以搵到佢哋嘅人，雖然佢哋唔知對方有冇死<br />\nTony冇辦法修復Benatar，喺Pepper同埋Banner嘅描述下佢哋估到Tony同Peter去咗Titan，Thor同Rocket負責去救Tony<br />\n<br />\n佢哋首先去到Nidavellia搵到Benatar嘅逃生艙，收到Tony嘅信息<br />\n跟住救返Tony，而Rocket對Tony嘅維修技術印象深刻，兩人一拍即合<br />\n<br />\n全部人返到AVG總部，Thor以為Carol係敵人，差啲打咗出手<br />\nSteve同Tony終於見返面<br />\n<br />\n想知再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T09:37:36.000Z","msg":"繼續吹"},{"pid":"edaccb667ca1ff1b5f8d9766e5589ac081f896fe","tid":1097072,"uid":195438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T09:39:48.000Z","msg":"一齊係泰坦星BBQ"},{"pid":"f41dca2b0e8b3084030bd5d491fb8e25caaacf4f","tid":1097072,"uid":192968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ad5ef5e8ae2b11447257e439825a4912e92c0b2","tid":1097072,"uid":29787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T07:01:45.000Z","msg":"就上不如大家估下戲入面有咩會出現，劇情會係點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我估隊長會拎起Thor把斧頭<br />\n<br />\n劇情會係去返之前咁多套戲改變個結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T15:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}